      "title": "Spacing",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The website uses a four-step spacing scale for layout. The examples below denote a class starting with <span class=\"roboto-mono\">.s</span> which stands for 'spacing'. The site replaces <span class=\"roboto-mono\">.s</span> with the default Tachyons margin and padding naming conventions but appends the spacing's <span class=\"roboto-mono\">rem</span> value. For example, <span class=\"roboto-mono\">.pr2</span> is equivalent to <span class=\"roboto-mono\">{ padding-right: 2rem; }</span>"
